---
title: Careers
layout: default
feature_image: "/img/splashes/prairie_1.jpeg"
---

<div class="relative mb-16">
  <div class="relative px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="prose prose-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 mx-auto">
      <p>
        We value attention to detail, cooperative and collaborative attitudes,
        and relevant knowledge and experience. We offer a flexible schedule,
        paid time off, professional development assistance, and a friendly and
        collegial work environment.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="bg-white py-8">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-md px-4 sm:max-w-3xl sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:max-w-7xl">
    <h2 class="text-base text-center font-semibold tracking-wider text-secondary-500 uppercase">
      Current Openings
    </h2>
    <div class="mt-5 prose prose-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 mx-auto">
      <p>
        To apply for an opening, please send your r&eacute;sum&eacute; and a cover
        letter to <a href="mailto:cbarnes@bsncpa.com" class="underline">Cristen
          Barnes</a>. <b>Buckley &amp; Sitzman, LLP</b> is an Equal Opportunity
        Employer and welcomes all qualified candidates.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div x-data="{shown: false}" x-intersect.once="shown = true">
      <div class="mt-12" x-show="shown" x-transition>
        <div class="auto-flow-fr grid-flow-row grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-y-16
          sm:gap-y-0 sm:gap-x-16">
          {%- for posting in collections.job_postings -%}
            <div class="flex flex-col justify-between bg-gray-50 shadow-xl p-8 rounded-lg">
              <div class="flex-1 flex-col space-y-8">
                <div class="text-xl text-center text-gray-800 leading-6 font-semibold space-y-1">
                  <h3>{{posting.name}}</h3>
                </div>
                {% if posting.image %}
                  <div class="aspect-w-3 aspect-h-2">
                    <img
                      src="{{posting.image}}"
                      alt="{{posting.name}}"
                      class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-md"
                    />
                  </div>
                {% endif %}
                <div class="prose text-gray-700">
                  {{ posting.body | markdown | safe }}
                </div>
              </div>
              {% if posting.link %}
                <div class="mt-16 flex justify-center">
                  <a
                    href="{{posting.link}}"
                    target="_blank"
                    class="inline-flex items-center uppercase py-3 px-4 rounded-md
                           hover:scale-105 transition ease-in-out bg-secondary-500
                           text-black font-medium focus:outline-none focus:ring-2
                           focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-secondary-400
                           focus:ring-offset-secondary-600"
                  >
                    Apply
                  </a>
                </div>
              {% endif %}
            </div>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="w-full my-12">
  <img class="mx-auto w-12" src="/assets/hex_logo.svg">
</div>

<div class="bg-white pb-16 px-6 sm:pb-24 lg:pb-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-md sm:max-w-3xl sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:max-w-7xl">
    <div class="mt-24 mx-auto max-w-prose">
      <p class="text-left text-xl text-gray-700">
        Ready to start the next step of your career with <b>Buckley &amp;
          Sitzman, LLP</b> and join one of the best accounting firms to work at
        in Lincoln?
      </p>
      <p class="mt-10 text-center">
        <a
          href="/contact-us"
          target="_blank"
          class="inline-flex items-center uppercase py-3 px-4 rounded-md
                 hover:scale-105 transition ease-in-out bg-secondary-500
                 text-black font-medium focus:outline-none focus:ring-2
                 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-secondary-400
                 focus:ring-offset-secondary-600"
        >
          Contact Us
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
